Invocation Name: cavaliers trivia
des:
This skill tests your knowledge of the Cleveland Cavaliers. If you don't know the answer, you may just learn something new.

You will be asked 5 questions and asked to select one 4 answers. Answer the question correctly, and Alexa gives you a point. If you don't Alexa will tell you the correct answer.

Designed and built by a fifth grader.
